# Intuition
Very easy approach to solve the problem with the help of single loop and hashmap

# Approach

* initiate a Map 
* enter all elements and its frequency
* inside of entry loop of map ,check
1. if k==0 , it means any element which is occuring more then twice will always have diff ==0 , ex- 1-1=0 , 15-15 =0 ...
2. else if map contains element + k , then pair++  

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
o(n)
- Space complexity:
o(n)

