```
- => 000110
. => 000111
/ => 01100
: => 001000
b => 001001
c => 011100
d => 011101
e => 0011
g => 001010
h => 001011
i => 011110
l => 01001
m => 011111
n => 00000
o => 01010
p => 00001
r => 00010
