# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
let num1 be a+bi, num2 be c+di

    (a +bi) * ( c+di)
    = (a*c-b*d) + (b*c +a*d)i

to parse the string to integer representation, first **find the "+" in each number**, seperate the substring

